---
title: Cheater Rotisserie Chicken and Gravy Dinner with Steamed Veggies and Smashed Potatoes
description: Tonight's dinner delivers on all the flavour of a roasted rotisserie chicken minus the fuss. Served with chive-studded potatoes to catch the super savoury gravy, this dish is a winner chicken dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-style-rotisserie-et-sauce-529c9913.jpg
